@startuml Sequence_API_Portfolio
title API Sequence - Load Portfolio Data

actor User
participant Browser
participant "React App" as React
participant "Vite Proxy" as Vite
participant "FastAPI" as API

User -> Browser: Visit website
Browser -> React: Load SPA
activate React

React -> React: Initialize Router
React -> React: Render Home Component

React -> Vite: GET /api/portfolio
activate Vite
Vite -> API: Proxy request
activate API
API -> API: Build PortfolioData
API --> Vite: JSON Response
deactivate API
Vite --> React: JSON Response
deactivate Vite

React -> React: Update State
React -> React: Render Sections
React --> Browser: Display Content
deactivate React
Browser --> User: Portfolio Page

@enduml
